Class GenericStack<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • blak3980.GenericStack<T>

  • public class GenericStack<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    A simple linked stack structure of GenericNode objects. Only the T data contained in the stack is visible through the standard stack methods.
    Author:
    Tyler Blakeley Blak3980@mylaurier.ca 090603980
